data.description: New Year-New Home, welcome to in Sterling Ranch located at the base of the breathtaking Rocky Mountain foothills. At just over 2300 sq ft finished & the potential to be over 3300 sq ft finished this Smart Home and HERS rated is sure to tick all those boxes. Upon entering you will notice a conveniently located office, half bath and large storage closet, extra wide LVP flooring, taller baseboards, pendant lighting in the kitchen, under counter lighting, gas range, full height backsplash with plenty of countertop space and don’t forget that central island. The great room is spacious & bright but what completes this room is the elegant stone surround gas fireplace for those cozy winter evenings. The sunroom is an added bonus on this model home, bringing in plenty of natural light. Upstairs notice the extra wide hallway, loft area for your enjoyment and of course the primary bedroom that has a bump out for a seating area. The primary bath has a quartz vanity, shower and soaking tub with power window treatment above, the walk in closet & a custom upgrade will accommodate all your needs. There are 2 further beds on this level, 1 well appointed full bath & laundry room with custom storage space, there's also ceiling fans throughout this home. The backyard has already been landscaped with indoor outdoor living in mind, fully fenced there is a screened in generous patio area for privacy, storage shed, window well coverings and lighting. There's extra length in the garage along with 220v & the optional use of solar panels. In Sterling Ranch by end of 2024 internet speeds here will be up to 8 gigabits per second. Amenities include free annual state park pass, pool, fitness center, clubhouse, playground, park & trails all built into the property taxes. This floorpan is thoughtfully designed to combine elegance & luxury together with hi-tech efficient features which will make this your new home. *assumable loan.
